. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.economist.com/blogs/graphicdetail/2012/12/daily-chart-19\">\"Pricing Sunshine\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Economist\" title=\"The Economist\">The Economist</a></i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2012-12-28</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Economist&amp;rft.atitle=Pricing+Sunshine&amp;rft.date=2012-12-28&amp;rft.au=Staff+writer&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fblogs%2Fgraphicdetail%2F2012%2F12%2Fdaily-chart-19&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASwanson%27s+law\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Swanson-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Swanson_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">R. M. Swanson (2006). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/pip.709/abstract\">\"A vision for crystalline silicon photovoltaics\"</a>. <i>Progress in Photovoltaics: Research and Applications</i>. <b>14</b>: 443\u2013453. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1002/pip.709\">10.1002/pip.709</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Progress+in+Photovoltaics%3A+Research+and+Applications&amp;rft.atitle=A+vision+for+crystalline+silicon+photovoltaics&amp;rft.volume=14&amp;rft.pages=443-453&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1002%2Fpip.709&amp;rft.au=R.+M.+Swanson&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1002%2Fpip.709%2Fabstract&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASwanson%27s+law\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:no